The X11 fonts for ${FULLPKGNAME} have been installed to

  ${FONTDIR}

You must add them to your X11 font paths with the
following command:

  xset +fp ${FONTDIR}

To enable this permanently when the X11 server is
started, add

  FontPath "${FONTDIR}"

in the "Files" section of your xorg.conf file.
